parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the auto idle stop system can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to restart, leaving the driver stranded in traffic, which can lead to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls when auto idle stop is engaged
the vehicle fails to restart after idle stop
error messages appear on the dashboard
the vehicle requires multiple attempts to restart
the vehicle restarts after a delay of 10-20 seconds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the keyless remote system can cause the vehicle to shut off while driving, leaving the driver stranded, which can lead to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts off while driving
error messages appear on the dashboard indicating "keyless remote not detected"
the vehicle requires specific actions to restart
such as putting the vehicle in park and pressing the start button.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine performance issues can cause the vehicle to reduce speed, lose power, or stall, which can lead to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The engine reduces speed
the vehicle loses power
the engine makes unusual noises
the engine warning light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery drainage system can cause the vehicle to fail to start, leaving the driver stranded and potentially causing safety concerns.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to start
the battery drains quickly
the vehicle requires frequent jump-starts or replacement of the battery.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and shifting issues can cause the vehicle to stall while idling, shift into neutral automatically, and stall when sitting at a light, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine shuts off while idling
the vehicle shifts into neutral automatically
the vehicle stalls when sitting at a light
the fuel pressure light and battery light come on when the engine shuts off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The camera issues can cause the backup camera to malfunction, making it difficult to see when reversing, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Moisture or liquid enters the camera
the camera is difficult to see when reversing
the camera malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Emission System and Electric Parking Brake Alarms
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The emission system and electric parking brake alarms can cause distractions while driving, leading to potential safety concerns.
symptoms: The emission system problem alarm and electric parking brake problem alarm constantly come on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The front sensor warning issues can cause distractions while driving, leading to potential safety concerns.
symptoms: The front sensor warning repeatedly goes off when stopped
especially in rainy conditions
the alert continues to go off when going from a full stop to moving
the alert restarts once the car comes to a full stop again.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure due to Rod Bearing Connection Failure

inability to shift into gear.

difficulty shifting gears.

stalling

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Software and electrical issues can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to safety hazards, distractions, and accidents.

stalling
loss of power.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Seizure Due to Manufacturing Defect
